<title>Sea, ice, snow, and the Inuit</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &#39;Sea, Ice, Snow, It&#39;s  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/may/30/canada-inuits-climate-change-impact-global-warming-melting-ice&#34;&gt;All Changing&lt;/a&gt;&#39;: Inuit Culture Struggles with Warming World.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
