<updated>2018-06-05T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Inauguration protesters</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/news/2018/05/31/victory-dissent-government-drops-charges-against-group-j20-protesters&#34;&gt;A judge dropped charges&lt;/a&gt; against some inauguration protesters because US prosecutors were shown to have violated their right to a fair trial.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
